{
  "stem": "8753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to hire the people to shred the wheat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is-- was another thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To work on the farm, to work in the fields, was something that if you worked in the fields, you were called a peasant.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you-- now, we spent every penny we had to the peasants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we didn't go to work in the fields.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Because it was shunned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to hire people to-- for all the work, shred the wheat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then so we used to make the flour from the wheat for our use.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And mostly we did it-- I don't really remember if he sold anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I doubt it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was for our own use.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have too many-- too much land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, we had a few-- we used to call it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what is the equal here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They were like strips of land that we owned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, the-- it made beautiful scenery to have a painting of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- each area-- by the way, there were rich people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, they owned a lot of land.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were called the [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They owned the land around the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the land was all together in the same area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The poorer people had a strip of land to one corner of the town and a strip of land in another.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Otherwise, if you had money, a few zlotys, you bought a strip of land, and that's how.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, each area was known of growing a certain-- let's say, one area was-- they grew potatoes there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The potatoes were growing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another corner of the-- of the town, a strip of land, the wheat was growing better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you understand?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
